@startuml
title ATM Control - User Interaction

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state "Waiting for PIN" as WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state "Waiting for Customer Choice" as WaitingForChoice
state Confiscating
state Ejecting

Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu

WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN, Card Stolen, Card Expired / Confiscate, Update Status

Confiscating --> Terminating : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated

Terminating --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time) [Closedown Not Requested]

WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected / Request Withdrawal, Display Wait
WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingTransfer : Transfer Selected / Request Transfer, Display Wait
WaitingForChoice --> ProcessingQuery : Query Selected / Request Query, Display Wait

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

Dispensing --> Printing : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt, Display Cash Dispensed, Confirm Cash Dispensed
Dispensing --> Ejecting : Insufficient Cash / Eject

Printing --> Ejecting : Receipt Printed / Eject

Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected / Display Ejected

@enduml
